Kari Patel. Kari, would you please introduce yourself?

5
00:00:23,188 --> 00:00:27,890
Hey, Brian. Thanks a bunch for having me. It's really great to be talking to you today.

6
00:00:28,431 --> 00:00:32,272
My name is Kari Patel, and as Brian said, I work at Obsidian Entertainment,

7
00:00:32,292 --> 00:00:34,853
where I am a game director and a senior narrative designer.

8
