00:21:29,242 --> 00:21:33,342
I mean, I guess it's, you know, what kind of, what kind of, I guess the biggest question

291
00:21:33,382 --> 00:21:35,963
is what is the experience that you want players to have?

292
00:21:36,543 --> 00:21:40,644
Like you know, what is, what is your elevator pitch of this is why you're going to play

293
00:21:40,684 --> 00:21:44,464
the game and this is, this is the promise of what we're offering with it.

294
00:21:46,925 --> 00:21:52,086
I feel like you almost, you start with the very, the very focused, well, the very high

295
00:21:52,126 --> 00:21:54,486
level stuff and you sort of build out as you go down.

296
00:21:54,546 --> 00:21:58,567
So you have that experience and you know, then you say, okay, well.

297
00:21:59,483 --> 00:22:03,404
You know, they're basic things like, OK, well, what platforms are we offering this on?

298
00:22:03,504 --> 00:22:04,904
You know, what's what's kind of the genre?

299
00:22:04,924 --> 00:22:07,845
Is this an RPG? Is this an action? Is this somewhere in between?

300
00:22:08,785 --> 00:22:09,905
You know, what kind of setting is this?

301
00:22:09,986 --> 00:22:13,486
Is this sci fi? Is this fantasy? Is this, you know, an existing IP?

302
00:22:15,127 --> 00:22:17,247
And, you know, kind of as you build out those questions,

303
00:22:17,467 --> 00:22:19,768
you're also thinking about I think the pillars are

304
00:22:20,828 --> 00:22:24,109
one of the things that should come very early in the process

305
00:22:24,709 --> 00:22:26,730
because, you know, your pillars are.

306
00:22:27,490 --> 00:22:30,591
The design goals and elements that support that basic experience.

307
00:22:31,792 --> 00:22:37,035
And you may massage how you frame them, how you word them.

308
00:22:37,655 --> 00:22:40,717
And as you're building out the specifications of the game,

309
00:22:40,737 --> 00:22:42,538
you may need to take a couple of checkpoints

310
00:22:42,598 --> 00:22:45,820
and say, OK, are these specifications,

311
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:49,202
are these different features that we want to invest in,

312
00:22:49,742 --> 00:22:51,163
is this still reflective of?

313
00:22:51,925 --> 00:22:56,199
The core experience and the pillars that we are saying support that core experience.

