00:23:53,714 --> 00:23:54,695
when it comes to writing

331
00:23:54,755 --> 00:23:56,316
as opposed to traditional prose fiction?

332
00:23:56,596 --> 00:23:57,937
I love that question because you mentioned

333
00:23:57,977 --> 00:23:59,257
you've done prose writing as well.

334
00:23:59,477 --> 00:24:00,678
That comes from Peter Varga.

335
00:24:01,739 --> 00:24:04,480
So I think, and again, this sort of varies depending on,

